title: Sun Rise Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Latin Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Simple place offering American Latin food. Breakfast menu vegan choices include a burrito, vegan chorizo, tofu pesto with tomato, tofu with veggies, and vegan French toast with fruit. Lunch/dinner vegan choices include fajitas, tamale, and veggie pupusa with spinach or zucchini.
